## Overview

This dashboard provides visualizations for Security Event from Symantec Endpoint Security.

The dashboard displays Counts of Security Event, Count of Suspected Breach and Devices Required Restart. It breaks down Events by Reason, Event by Outcome, Scan by Peripheral Device Vendor, Scan by Peripheral Device, Scan by Type, Event by Incident State, Event by Incident Resolution and Event by Security Level. It displays the Number of Scan over Time. A Peripheral Device Class controller has been added to facilitate interactive data exploration.
